## Run the whole stack in Docker

```bash
uv run {{ cli_name }} stack up        # nginx web on http://localhost:8080 + backend{% if database == 'postgres' %} + postgres{% endif %}
uv run {{ cli_name }} stack logs      # follow logs        stack ps → health
uv run {{ cli_name }} stack down      # stop (--volumes wipes data)
